FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1780989354
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FMrs Pinkney suffered fatal head and
OL,7,Fneck injuries in the crash on a 30mph
OL,8,Fstretch of road near the MetroCentre
OL,9,Fin Gateshead in July 2022.
OL,11,FRoberts, from Darlington, was found
OL,12,Fguilty of causing death by dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving and jailed for 27 months in
OL,14,FApril, but Mrs Pinkney's family said
OL,15,Fthey "did not want him to go to prison
OL,16,Ffor doing his job".
OL,18,FHe was also convicted of causing Mr
OL,19,FPinkney, who suffered a bleed on the
OL,20,Fbrain and multiple fractures, serious
OL,21,Finjury by dangerous driving.
OL,26,@wD@FOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
