CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1780989354
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FToday (Friday 5 June), Roberts
OL,7,Fappealed against the length of his
OL,8,Fsentence at the Court of Appeal in
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FHis barrister Luke Ponte KC said in
OL,12,Fwritten submissions the sentence was
OL,13,F"manifestly excessive" and the judge
OL,14,Fdid not "reflect the exceptional
OL,15,Fmitigation", including that he was
OL,16,Fresponding to an emergency and had a
OL,17,F"lifetime of remarkable public
OL,18,Fservice".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@VO]vD@IOUwD@KO]yD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1780989354
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FAt the end of the hearing, three
OL,7,Fappeal judges ruled the sentence
OL,8,Fshould be reduced and suspended,
OL,9,Fmeaning Roberts can be released from
OL,10,Fcustody.
OL,12,FIn their judgment, Lady Justice
OL,13,FAndrews, sitting with Mr Justice Jay
OL,14,Fand Mrs Justice Thornton, said it was
OL,15,Fan "exceptional case".
OL,17,FLady Justice Andrews said Roberts had
OL,18,Fbeen a serving police officer who had
OL,19,Fresponded to many incidents over his
OL,20,Fcareer.
OL,26,@wD@DOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1780989354
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FShe continued: "This was not a case of
OL,7,Fprolonged dangerous driving."
OL,9,FThe court was told there is no real
OL,10,Frisk Roberts will reoffend and that
OL,11,Fcustody had a significant impact on
OL,12,Fhis family, including his disabled
OL,13,Fdaughter.
OL,15,F"We have concluded the sentence can
OL,16,Fand should be suspended," Lady Justice
OL,17,FAndrews said.
OL,26,@nD@POUoD@]O]wD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
