OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1780989354
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FRoberts, who appeared at the hearing
OL,7,Fby video-link from prison, appeared
OL,8,Femotional and could be seen wiping his
OL,9,Feyes as the judges gave their decision.
OL,11,FThe judges quashed the original
OL,12,Fsentence of 27 months in prison and
OL,13,Fimposed a two-year sentence, suspended
OL,14,Ffor 18 months.
OL,16,FDuring Roberts' sentencing, Mr and Mrs
OL,17,FPinkney's daughter said the family
OL,18,F"don't blame the officer for what
OL,19,Fhappened" and said they did not want
OL,20,FRoberts to be imprisoned.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1780989354
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read
OL,7,Fduring the sentencing hearing, Dawn
OL,8,FHunter-Pinkney said: "For a long time
OL,9,Fwe were angry but the more we hear
OL,10,Fabout why the officer was driving the
OL,11,Fway he was, the more we understand."
OL,13,FThe statement continued: "We don't
OL,14,Fwant him to go to prison for doing his
OL,15,Fjob.
OL,17,F"We do accept this is a very tragic
OL,18,Faccident with a very tragic outcome,
OL,19,Fbut sending the officer to prison
OL,20,Fwon't bring mam back."
OL,26,@pD@VOUsD@dO]uD@ZOUyD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1780989354
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FRoberts was suspended from Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice, with the force's Assistant
OL,8,FChief Constable Andy Hill saying after
OL,9,Fthe sentencing: "I reiterate my
OL,10,Fprevious comments in recognising that
OL,11,Fno words will make the pain of Mr
OL,12,FPinkney, his family and anyone
OL,13,Fimpacted by this tragic incident, any
OL,14,Feasier.
OL,16,F"On behalf of Northumbria Police, I
OL,17,Fwish to express my sincere condolences
OL,18,Ffor your loss and our thoughts very
OL,19,Fmuch continue to be with you at this
OL,20,Ftime."
OL,26,@qD@QOUxD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
