OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cto be freed from prison after appeal
OL,6,FRoberts was dismissed without notice
OL,7,Ffrom the force following a misconduct
OL,8,Fhearing in April where there was a
OL,9,Ffinding of gross misconduct.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/9
